{
  "texts": [
    "Our study is limited in several ways that suggest directions for future research.",
    "First, because we were examining multiple conditions in multiple trials across multiple tests, we prompted the LLMs in a way that encouraged them to provide their final answer in a way that was easily retrievable with computer code.",
    "In particular, we asked the LLM to provide its final answer in curly brackets {}.",
    "However, in doing so, we may have altered the behavior of the LLM, given that any alterations to the input sequence can substantially alter results.",
    "Second, to facilitate the investigation, we used code to automatically retrieve the final answer and gave the LLM no opportunities to improve upon its response to the initial prompt."
  ]
}